[
  {
    "text": "- What about free will?",
    "start": "1640",
    "end": "3400"
  },
  {
    "text": "- Free will is also a nice exercise.",
    "start": "3400",
    "end": "7410"
  },
  {
    "text": "Free will is an illusion that we,",
    "start": "7410",
    "end": "10340"
  },
  {
    "text": "A.I. people are gonna solve.",
    "start": "10340",
    "end": "12403"
  },
  {
    "text": "- (Interviewer) So, what do you think,",
    "start": "13923",
    "end": "15430"
  },
  {
    "text": "once we solve it, that\nsolution will look like?",
    "start": "15430",
    "end": "17880"
  },
  {
    "text": "Once we've put it in the page?",
    "start": "17880",
    "end": "19380"
  },
  {
    "text": "- (Guest) It's going to look like...",
    "start": "19381",
    "end": "20214"
  },
  {
    "text": "First of all, it will look like a machine.",
    "start": "20214",
    "end": "22746"
  },
  {
    "text": "A machine that acts as though",
    "start": "22746",
    "end": "25190"
  },
  {
    "text": "it has free will.",
    "start": "25190",
    "end": "27050"
  },
  {
    "text": "It communicates with\nother machines as though",
    "start": "27050",
    "end": "29699"
  },
  {
    "text": "they have free will,",
    "start": "29700",
    "end": "31650"
  },
  {
    "text": "and you wouldn't be able\nto tell the difference",
    "start": "31650",
    "end": "34000"
  },
  {
    "text": "between a machine that does\nand a machine that doesn't",
    "start": "34000",
    "end": "36704"
  },
  {
    "text": "have free will.",
    "start": "36704",
    "end": "37833"
  },
  {
    "text": "- (Interviewer) So, the\nillusion, it propagates",
    "start": "39485",
    "end": "40318"
  },
  {
    "text": "the illusion of free will amongst",
    "start": "40318",
    "end": "42470"
  },
  {
    "text": "the other machines?",
    "start": "42470",
    "end": "43551"
  },
  {
    "text": "- (Guest) And faking it is having it.",
    "start": "43551",
    "end": "46263"
  },
  {
    "text": "Okay?",
    "start": "47220",
    "end": "48053"
  },
  {
    "text": "That's what true\nintelligence is all about.",
    "start": "48053",
    "end": "49650"
  },
  {
    "text": "Faking intelligence is intelligence,",
    "start": "49650",
    "end": "51363"
  },
  {
    "text": "because it's not easy to fake.",
    "start": "51363",
    "end": "55590"
  },
  {
    "text": "It's very hard to fake, and you can only",
    "start": "55590",
    "end": "58420"
  },
  {
    "text": "fake if you have it.",
    "start": "58420",
    "end": "60158"
  },
  {
    "text": "- (laughs)",
    "start": "60159",
    "end": "62409"
  },
  {
    "text": "That's such a beautiful statement.",
    "start": "63530",
    "end": "65960"
  },
  {
    "text": "(laughs)",
    "start": "65960",
    "end": "68043"
  },
  {
    "text": "You can't fake it, if you don't have it.",
    "start": "70368",
    "end": "72896"
  },
  {
    "text": "(laughs)",
    "start": "72896",
    "end": "73729"
  }
]